CREATE TABLE BS_COHORT_DISTRIBUTION (

GENDER CHAR(10) NULL,
ADDRESS_LINE_1 CHAR(10) NULL,
ADDRESS_LINE_2 CHAR(10) NULL,
ADDRESS_LINE_3 CHAR(10) NULL,
ADDRESS_LINE_4 CHAR(10) NULL,
ADDRESS_LINE_5 CHAR(10) NULL,

DATE_OF_DEATH CHAR(10) NULL,
TELEPHONE_NUMBER_HOME CHAR(10) NULL,
TELEPHONE_NUMBER_HOME_FROM_DT CHAR(10) NULL,
TELEPHONE_NUMBER_MOB CHAR(10) NULL,
TELEPHONE_NUMBER_MOB_FROM_DT CHAR(10) NULL,
EMAIL_ADDRESS_HOME CHAR(10) NULL,
EMAIL_ADDRESS_HOME_FROM_DT CHAR(10) NULL,

)
